      "ocr_text": "G RO U P 250 Massachusetts Ave NW, Suite 400 | Washington, DC 20001\nOctober 2, 2025\nSecretary of the Senate\nOffice of Public Records\n232 Hart Senate Office Building\nWashington, DC 20510\nRe: Senator Richard Blumenthal\nDear Madam Secretary:\nWe are writing on behalf of Senator Richard Blumenthal to file an amendment to his periodic transaction\nreport (\u201cPTR\u201d) filed on September 12, 2025.\nThe Peter L. Malkin Family 2000 LLC transaction listed on page 1, line 7 of this PTR should be amended\nto read as follows:\nSpouse Sera Prognostics | Sale 8/14/25 $1,001-\nInc-A (Stock) $15,000\n(SERA)\nPlease do not hesitate to contact us should you have any questions. Thank you for your attention to this\nmatter.\nSincerely,\nKate Sawyer Keane\nCounsel to Senator Richard Blumenthal",
